description:
This is a 37 minute workout called 'Calm - Ease | Guided Meditation by Thich Nhat Hanh' from the channel Plum Village.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: A great guided meditation offered by Thay to help us cultivate calm, ease and joy.
